<h1>5 Best Fall 2020 Anime to Watch + First Impressions</h1>

<p>Today, with <a href="https://gogoanime.city/">GogoAnime</a>, we review the list of 15 Fall 2019 Anime that are most anticipated by the audience.</p>

<p>Just a few more days, the fall 2019 anime will officially kick off. In this season, we are extremely excited to welcome the return of a series of blockbusters with new seasons such as My Hero Academia, The Seven Deadly Sins, SAO, etc. and new high-quality anime series. What are the most anticipated movies?</p>

<h2>15. Bokutachi wa Benkyou ga Dekinai season 2 (We Never Learn season 2)</h2>

<p>The film&#39;s content is about Yuiga - a student from a difficult family, who is aiming to win a scholarship. The school agreed to give him a scholarship if he could fulfill a &quot;super easy&quot; condition of tutoring two beautiful female classmates in order to help them get into the school they wanted.</p>

<p>Both of these girls are natural geniuses, but sadly: The natural genius wants to enter art school and the literary prodigy wants to enter literature school&hellip; Will Yuiga do it? What do these two girls achieve?</p>

<h2>14. BEASTAR</h2>

<p>The content of the film takes place in the world of carnivores and herbivores, a place filled with hope and love but also filled with anxiety. Regoshi is a wolf and member of the drama club of Cherryton Academy, and despite being a wolf, he is very sensitive. The manga follows the teenage life of Regoshi and many other animals.</p>

<h2>13.&nbsp;Stand My Heroes: Piece of Truth</h2>

<p>The film is set in the modern city of Tokyo. Matori, the narcotics control unit of investigators under the Ministry of Health, Labor and Welfare. The main character, who has the unique characteristic of being resistant to the effects of drugs. When she ends up working in the unit she looks for staff from investigators, idols, writers, genius high school students, top designers, housekeepers, underground doctors and others to Form teams of ikemen heroes for different missions.</p>

<h2>12. Ahiru no Sora</h2>

<p>The content of the film revolves around Sora Kurumatani 15 years old and only 1.49m tall, but he loves basketball. That&#39;s why he joined the school&#39;s club and began to face difficult challenges.</p>

<h2>11.&nbsp;Watashi, Nouryoku wa Heikinchi de tte Itta yo ne!</h2>

<p>When the eldest daughter of the Duke of Ascham, Adele von Ascham, was 10 years old, she remembered everything after a headache. In her previous life, she was Kurihara Misato, an 18-year-old Japanese who lost her life saving a little girl, and then she met a God&hellip; Someone who somehow was burdened by the expectations of many people around her, Misato, who did not She could live as she wanted, begging God.</p>

<p>&ldquo;In my next life, please make my learning average!&rdquo;</p>

<h2>10.&nbsp;Kono Oto Tomare!: Sounds of Life</h2>

<p>Since the seniors had all graduated, Takezou became the only member of the Koto club (a traditional Japanese stringed instrument). Unwritten rule: Each club must have 2 or more members to be allowed to operate! Now facing the danger of having to close the club, how does Takezou - a sentimental, autistic, friendless young lady - must manage to continue maintaining the club!?</p>

<h2>9. Assassins Pride</h2>

<p>The film has content that takes place in a world where only people from noble families have mana to fight against monsters. Kuufa is a noble born into the family of a duke who is sent to tutor a young young girl named Merida. If Merida wasn&#39;t gifted with mana, Kūfa would secretly teach her to assassinate.</p>

<h2>8.&nbsp;Shokugeki no Souma: Shin no Sara</h2>

<p>Perhaps this will be the last season of Shokugeki no Souma. The unfinished ending on the manga will be adapted into the most complete anime version.</p>

<h2>7. Nanatsu no Taizai: Kamigami no Gekirin</h2>

<p>The third season of the Nanatsu no Taizai anime series.</p>

<h2>6.&nbsp;Aikatsu on Parade!</h2>

<p>Raki Kiseki is a second year high school girl whose goal is to transfer to Star Harmony Academy to become an idol. However, when she used the Aikatsu Pass she received from her older sister (an Aikatsu engineer), something mysterious happened.</p>

<p>Many doors appear before her eyes and when she opens them, she meets Aikatsu idols she has never known before, such as Yume Nijino (Aikatsu Star!). Raki vows to design her own haute couture gown and perform on stage.</p>

<h2>5. Fate/Grand Order: Zettai Majuu Sensen Babylonia</h2>

<p>The film content will adapt the story &quot;Dai Nana Tokuiten Zettai Majū Sensen Babylonia&quot; (Order VII: The Absolute Frontline in the War Against the Demonic Beasts: Babylonia) in the game.</p>

<h2>4. Psycho-Pass 3</h2>

<p>In the not-too-distant future, then, it will be possible to immediately determine the will and character of each person. This information is recorded and processed, and the term &ldquo;Psycho-pass&rdquo; is the standard by which an individual is measured. The story revolves around &quot;Execution Officer&quot; Kougami Shinya, who is assigned to manage crime in that world.</p>

<h2>3. My Hero Academia season 4</h2>

<p>In a world populated with superhumans, the superhero-loving Izuku Midoriya is without power. However, after the Quirkless dreamer Izuku inherits the powers of the world&#39;s best superhero, All Might, his hopes of becoming the top hero are now possible. Once enrolled in the high school for heroes, U.A., Izuku soon discovers being a hero is much more complicated than it appears.</p>

<h2>2. Chihayafuru season 3</h2>

<p>Chihaya&#39;s whole life and dream was just to see her sister become the most famous model in Japan&hellip;.but then, when a quiet, quiet student named Arata told her that &quot;Dreams can only be achieved by yourself, not taken from others.&quot;</p>

<p>Arata is a boy who enjoys playing the traditional Japanese card game Hyakunin Isshu that Chihaya enjoys greatly, and thanks to Arata, Chihaya discovered a passion for it. And she had a dream of her own, the dream of becoming &quot;Karuta Queen&quot; Chihayafuru has won 2 Manga Taisho awards.</p>

<h2>1. Sword Art Online: Alicization &ndash; War of Underworld</h2>

<p>Believe that this list will help you choose the right anime, take the time to focus on watching the anime that is more suitable for you. What are you waiting for, let&#39;s go with GoGoanime to welcome a truly exciting Anime Fall 2021.</p>
